    public interface OaamBaseElementA
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject
    A representation of the model object 'Oaam Base Element A'. This is the base class for every instantiable element in the model. Most important it defines that every model element has a name and an id

    The following features are supported:

    • Id
    • Name
    • Style
    • Attributes
    • Documentation
    • Modified
    • Modifier
    • Trace Link
    See Also:
    CommonPackage.getOaamBaseElementA()
